<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<StimulusTransportBase xmlns:i="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="http://schemas.datacontract.org/2004/07/Tobii.Studio.Design.Transport">
  <Key>3e005bc6-2349-4383-a8c6-b729b60531f8</Key>
  <Value i:type="InstructionsStimulusTransport">
    <Channel>WpfChannel</Channel>
    <Id>85d26834-6578-4e39-bb95-1e8cd1b6cf4d</Id>
    <Name>Chatgpt-3</Name>
    <BackgroundColor xmlns:d2p1="http://schemas.datacontract.org/2004/07/Tobii.ApplicationFoundation">
      <d2p1:A>255</d2p1:A>
      <d2p1:B>211</d2p1:B>
      <d2p1:G>211</d2p1:G>
      <d2p1:R>211</d2p1:R>
    </BackgroundColor>
    <IsMouseCursorVisible>false</IsMouseCursorVisible>
    <Margin>4</Margin>
    <Markup>&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd"&gt;&lt;html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" /&gt;&lt;title&gt;Untitled&lt;/title&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;Introducing the Camii Mia Women's Winter Slim Fit Fleece Jeans - your cozy companion through the cold season! These stylish jeans are specially designed with a mid-rise and a comfortable, skinny leg silhouette that flatters your figure while maintaining a snug and secure fit. Crafted with an inner lining of soft fleece, they promise to keep you warm and toasty without adding bulk.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;Key Features:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Warmth and Comfort: Enjoy the feel of soft fleece lining that offers extra warmth during chilly days. The jeans' thick material ensures you stay cozy no matter the weather.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Flattering Fit: Tailored with a slim fit and a skinny leg design, these jeans highlight your curves and elongate your legs, making them perfect for any casual or semi-formal outfit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Classic Styling: Equipped with the traditional five-pocket design, a zip fly, and a button closure, these jeans combine convenience with timeless fashion.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Easy Care: Machine washable for hassle-free maintenance. Keep your jeans looking new without extra effort.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Quality Craftsmanship: Proudly made in China, Camii Mia jeans reflect simplicity and elegance through excellent craftsmanship and durable materials.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;Sizing Tips:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Choose the Right Size: These jeans are designed with a snug fit. For optimal comfort and to accommodate the fleece lining, consider purchasing a size larger than your usual size.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Stretch and Fit: The fabric offers some stretch to conform to your body, ensuring a flattering fit that moves with you. The waistband is less stretchy, so choosing the right waist size is crucial for the best fit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;Perfect For:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Winter Wear: Ideal for keeping warm in cold climates without sacrificing style.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Versatile Fashion: Dress them up with a chic blouse and boots or keep it casual with a sweater and sneakers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;Upgrade your winter wardrobe with the Camii Mia Women's Winter Slim Fit Fleece Jeans, where fashion meets function in the coziest way!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.15;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Courier New';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 48px;color: #000000;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</Markup>
    <Resolution xmlns:d2p1="http://schemas.datacontract.org/2004/07/Tobii.ApplicationFoundation">
      <d2p1:Height>1080</d2p1:Height>
      <d2p1:Width>1920</d2p1:Width>
    </Resolution>
    <SupportsReadingResearch>true</SupportsReadingResearch>
  </Value>
</StimulusTransportBase>